name: ui
description: ElevenLabs UI is a component library and custom registry built on top of shadcn/ui to help you build multimodal agents faster.
readme_summary: ElevenLabs UI is a React component library and CLI tool built on shadcn/ui, designed to accelerate the development of multimodal agent and audio applications. It provides pre-built, customizable UI components and simplifies their integration into Next.js projects.
key_features: Pre-built, customizable React components for agent & audio applications
CLI for easy component installation in Next.js projects
Supports installation of all components or specific components
Provides components like orbs, waveforms, voice agents, and audio players
primary_use_case: Accelerating the development of audio and agentic applications by providing pre-built, customizable UI components and a CLI for easy integration.
cover_image_prompt: A skilled artisan in a futuristic workshop, effortlessly assembling intricate audio waveforms and glowing agent avatars from a palette of digital building blocks. The artisan uses a magical brush, painting vibrant sound waves and interactive agent interfaces onto a large, responsive screen. Subtle UI elements and code snippets float around the workshop, indicating the underlying technology. The scene is bathed in a soft, creative glow, with the 'ElevenLabs UI' logo subtly integrated into a blueprint. The overall style is a clean, 3D isometric illustration, emphasizing ease of use and creative power.

name: QtNotepad
description: Notepad-tool, support english and russian langs and text-formats
readme_summary: Qt-Notepad is a simple text editor built with PyQt6 and QSS, offering features like text formatting, search and replace, and language switching for English and Russian.
primary_use_case: A user-friendly text editing application with basic formatting and multilingual support.
cover_image_prompt: A friendly, anthropomorphic quill pen diligently writing on a scroll, with glowing digital particles of text flowing from the pen's tip onto the scroll. Beside the quill, a small, stylized book opens, showing pages with both English and Russian alphabets. In the background, subtle, abstract UI elements resembling a clean text editor interface are visible. The overall mood is creative and productive, with soft, warm lighting. The art style should be a charming 3D illustration with clear outlines and a focus on the interaction between the traditional writing tool and digital elements, representing the Qt-Notepad's functionality.

name: Zendra-password-generator
readme_summary: This repository provides a modified password generator with a graphical user interface (GUI) built using PyQt6. It offers multi-threaded password generation for faster results, along with various customization options, saving capabilities, and language support.
key_features: Copy button and save file button
primary_use_case: Generating strong, customizable passwords with a user-friendly graphical interface.
cover_image_prompt: A whimsical, steampunk-inspired automaton meticulously assembling intricate keys from a stream of digital data. The automaton's gears whir and steam gently rises as it selects specific components from the data flow, representing multi-threaded generation. On a small, integrated screen, different key designs are previewed, showcasing customization options. A polished, finished key is presented on a velvet cushion, ready to be copied or saved. Subtle glowing circuit patterns are etched into the automaton's metallic body, and the repository name 'Zendra' is subtly embossed on its base. The scene is set in a cozy workshop with warm, ambient lighting, rendered in a detailed 3D isometric illustration style.
